{"tid":1747728,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"投票問題！","createTime":"2019-11-23T10:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T11:27:09.000Z","uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e142950574a47c5705d47d0898819c8b75ab790","tid":1747728,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"想帶埋坐輪椅既老人家去投票，會帶埋工人陪同，想知佢投票既流程係點？個工人可唔可以陪同佢一齊？"},{"pid":"bcc1b0ca9afabce2b44fca13aafdcbe099450deb","tid":1747728,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:54:33.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"6ee5c29a420b52943d15829d093f0a5d72e11d34","tid":1747728,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:56:44.000Z","msg":"應該可以"},{"pid":"d101edabb221a8bbf063aed25c766e69aec6e037","tid":1747728,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無發現。<br />\n我地好似忽略咗班少數族裔選民？<br />\n先唔講選舉有無用<br />\n但作為社會一分子，我地唔係應該俾足夠既選舉資訊啲少數族裔，去選自己心儀既候選人？<br />\n<br />\n我地好似有樣嘢無做？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec053e8aeb7377488a08592a5e29600c35a9ae82","tid":1747728,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"入到去有工作人員帶佢<br />\n<br />\n申利以前係票站做過工作人"},{"pid":"1a283a356753b6e2578f37e79e97e282cea95333","tid":1747728,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"發言人說：「是次選舉約九成半的投票站可方便行動不便或使用輪椅的選民進出。在可行情況下，選舉事務處會在投票站加設臨時斜道，使有關投票站可供行動不便的選民使用。」<br />\n <br />\n  隨投票通知卡夾附的投票站位置圖，清楚列明該投票站是否方便行動不便或使用輪椅的選民進出。<br />\n <br />\n  他補充：「行動不便或使用輪椅的選民如被編配往不方便他們出入的投票站，可以在明日（十一月十九日）或之前（即最少在投票日五天前），透過選舉熱線（2891 1001）、傳真（2891 1180）或電郵（reoenq@reo.gov.hk）向選舉事務處申請重新編配到另一個投票站。如情況許可，選舉事務處會應要求安排復康巴士，接載他們來往投票站。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/18/P2019111800637.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F18%2FP2019111800637.htm&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpInMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=5331f30d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/18/P2019111800637.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bc3cbafb4230f12bb238c2aef53de9bf0dc86197","tid":1747728,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec053e8aeb7377488a08592a5e29600c35a9ae82","tid":1747728,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"入到去有工作人員帶佢<br />\n<br />\n申利以前係票站做過工作人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"係咪優先唔使排隊？"},{"pid":"8cc5522a0280d956c5381ab71e1fe2c5219901d7","tid":1747728,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEbiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEbiS</a>"},{"pid":"01be159cb47a88df27794de1f4a401917191a36a","tid":1747728,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc3cbafb4230f12bb238c2aef53de9bf0dc86197","tid":1747728,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec053e8aeb7377488a08592a5e29600c35a9ae82","tid":1747728,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"入到去有工作人員帶佢<br />\n<br />\n申利以前係票站做過工作人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"係咪優先唔使排隊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:27:09.000Z","msg":"咁我唔記得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,你試下到時問下票站既人"}]}